query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS scenario_strategies (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  scenarioId INT NOT NULL,
  componentCode VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  strategy ENUM('replace','rehabilitate','defer','do_nothing') NOT NULL,
  actionYear INT NOT NULL,
  deferralYears INT DEFAULT 0,
  strategyCost DECIMAL(15,2) NOT NULL,
  presentValueCost DECIMAL(15,2),
  lifeExtension INT,
  conditionImprovement INT,
  riskReduction DECIMAL(5,2),
  failureCostAvoided DECIMAL(15,2),
  maintenanceSavings DECIMAL(15,2),
  priorityScore DECIMAL(10,4),
  selected INT DEFAULT 0,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  updatedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
)
